title: Child Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a young person with a medium-dark skin tone. It's often used to depict children, youth, or family members.
apple_vendor_description: The child emoji with a medium-dark skin tone on Apple devices is rendered with a friendly, open expression and gentle, rounded features. Apple's characteristic realistic lighting and smooth gradients give the child a warm, approachable appearance, showcasing a sense of youthful innocence and joy. This versatile emoji is perfect for conveying familial love, representing children, or adding a touch of youthful spirit to conversations.
